\lim_{n\to \infty } \frac{1+\frac12+......+\frac1n}{\ln n}
\ln n
 \displaystyle\lim_{n\to \infty } \frac{1+\frac12+......+\frac1n}{\ln n}=\displaystyle\lim_{n\to \infty } \frac{\frac1{n+1}}{\ln (n+1)-\ln n}\\ =\displaystyle\lim_{n\to \infty } \frac{\frac1{n+1}}{\ln \frac {(n+1)}n}\\ =\displaystyle\lim_{n\to \infty } \frac{\frac{-1}{(n+1)^2}}{\frac1{(n+1)}-\frac 1n}\\ =\displaystyle\lim_{n\to \infty } \frac{\frac{-1}{(n+1)^2}}{\frac{-1}{n(n+1)}}=1\\ 
\gamma
\epsilon_n
n\to\infty
 1+\frac12+......+\frac1n=\ln n+\gamma+\epsilon_n 
